articles.author: Stefanie Payne
articles.title: Five Facts About NASA’s Moon Bound Technology - NASA
articles.description: NASA is sending revolutionary technologies to the Moon aboard Intuitive Machines’ second lunar delivery as part of the agency’s CLPS (Commercial Lunar Payload Services) initiative and Artemis campaign to establish a long-term presence on the lunar surface.
